{"tid":336824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逾80年歷史嘉頓中心擬清拆重建　地標鐘樓或成絕響","createTime":"2017-07-26T17:48:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-01T06:33:38.000Z","uid":31208,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2b71a0e6e29a0ed1626a04f8019776376ae42121","tid":336824,"uid":31208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T17:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/107300/thumbnail/8b109f04e211f307fbbb67ed6887ee0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F107300%2Fthumbnail%2F8b109f04e211f307fbbb67ed6887ee0c.jpg&h=ddd34bab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/107300/%E9%80%BE80%E5%B9%B4%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E5%98%89%E9%A0%93%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E6%93%AC%E6%B8%85%E6%8B%86%E9%87%8D%E5%BB%BA-%E5%9C%B0%E6%A8%99%E9%90%98%E6%A8%93%E6%88%96%E6%88%90%E7%B5%95%E9%9F%BF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F107300%2F%25E9%2580%25BE80%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B2%25E5%2598%2589%25E9%25A0%2593%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583%25E6%2593%25AC%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%258B%2586%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%25BB%25BA-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%25A8%2599%25E9%2590%2598%25E6%25A8%2593%25E6%2588%2596%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25B5%2595%25E9%259F%25BF&d=WlT4IkR%2BoRGBR7dGzPHsXZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=37057ecd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/107300/%E9%80%BE80%E5%B9%B4%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E5%98%89%E9%A0%93%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E6%93%AC%E6%B8%85%E6%8B%86%E9%87%8D%E5%BB%BA-%E5%9C%B0%E6%A8%99%E9%90%98%E6%A8%93%E6%88%96%E6%88%90%E7%B5%95%E9%9F%BF</a><br />\n<br />\n1930年代落成的嘉頓中心，見證著深水埗區發展，頂層的嘉頓鐘樓更在不少港人的心中留下深刻印象。不過這幢擁有逾80年歷史的地標，或許敵不過時代巨輪推進，步入終章。<br />\n<br />\n嘉頓有限公司向城規會申請，將嘉頓中心重建成一幢包括3層地庫、25層高的大樓，提供烹飪培訓課程和餐廳，以及將部分的辦公室出租。<br />\n<br />\n嘉頓公司回覆稱，重建計劃仍在初步構思及研究中，當未來有進一步資訊，會再作補充。<br />\n重建後有10層辦公室可出租<br />\n<br />\n城規會的文件顯示，申請人嘉頓有限公司擬將位於深水埗青山道58號的嘉頓中心，由「住宅(甲類)7」改建為「商店及服務行業、食肆、辦公室及學校」，提供25層高的大樓，包括3層地庫，總地盤面積為1,148平方米。<br />\n<br />\n申請人表示，重建後的大樓會提供餐廳或咖啡室、與烹飪有關的培訓課程以及辦公室，位於11至20樓的樓層單位將會租出。"},{"pid":"474404f91ddc737976f0b48a4389f6ed7bc1eac0","tid":336824,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T06:14:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/tpb/tc/plan_application/Attachment/20170725/s16_A_K5_782_0_gist.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Ftpb%2Ftc%2Fplan_application%2FAttachment%2F20170725%2Fs16_A_K5_782_0_gist.pdf&d=WlT4IkR%2BoRGBR7dGzPHsXZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=13cdd9ad\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.info.gov.hk/tpb/tc/plan_application/Attachment/20170725/s16_A_K5_782_0_gist.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n入面有圖則<br />\n<br />\n想問下點解12/f-21/f 面積縮到咁細？感覺上好嘥位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：對建築／工程一竅不通 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1481db8f9df4e3b8fe6715089fabd651026f3cd2","tid":336824,"uid":2771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T06:27:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/tpb/tc/plan_application/Attachment/20170725/s16_A_K5_782_0_gist.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Ftpb%2Ftc%2Fplan_application%2FAttachment%2F20170725%2Fs16_A_K5_782_0_gist.pdf&d=WlT4IkR%2BoRGBR7dGzPHsXZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=13cdd9ad\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.info.gov.hk/tpb/tc/plan_application/Attachment/20170725/s16_A_K5_782_0_gist.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n入面有圖則<br />\n<br />\n想問下點解12/f-21/f 面積縮到咁細？感覺上好嘥位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：對建築／工程一竅不通 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要顧大廈外型嘛"},{"pid":"37a0a73ba0b2c60d6cefe5f79d32725b9677283c","tid":336824,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T06:33:38.000Z","msg":"住左咁多年深水埗唔覺有咩咁值得留戀<br />\n同個堆7層公屋一撚樣唔知留黎做乜"}]}